WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
1. THREE RED FLARES SIGHTED IN 25-58N 065-55W
   AT 190100Z OCT. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
   TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO U.S. COAST GUARD SAN JUAN,
   PHONE: 787 289 2041, E-MAIL: SSJCC@USCG.MIL.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2599/13.
